00:42:36.785 --> 00:42:38.060
is like, oh.

00:42:38.060 --> 00:42:40.760
There's a saying where, I
wish I was rich so then people

00:42:40.760 --> 00:42:41.930
would listen to me.

00:42:41.930 --> 00:42:45.980
So people pay attention
because they became wealthy.

00:42:45.980 --> 00:42:48.230
And they kind of popularized
the idea of the engineer,

00:42:48.230 --> 00:42:50.690
and they gave a lot of
respect to the engineer,

00:42:50.690 --> 00:42:52.230
because now they make money.

00:42:52.230 --> 00:42:55.190
But in the past, like in the
