00:43:08.690 --> 00:43:12.238
In the '70s, being a
nerd was being a nerd.

00:43:12.238 --> 00:43:13.780
Nowadays, being a
nerd is like, damn,

00:43:13.780 --> 00:43:14.385
he might be a billionaire--

00:43:14.385 --> 00:43:15.552
I'm going to be nice to him.

00:43:19.760 --> 00:43:23.020
Now it's cool to be
