00:46:40.060 --> 00:46:42.610
In this great groups
model, he creates

00:46:42.610 --> 00:46:46.030
great groups within DARPA, and
then that leadership, as well,

00:46:46.030 --> 00:46:47.420
and moves that forward.

00:46:47.420 --> 00:46:52.540
And so he's obviously using his
