mutually with doing well

00:57:35.290 --> 00:57:36.832
for yourself and
for other people.

00:57:36.832 --> 00:57:38.290
I think that there's
a lot of value

00:57:38.290 --> 00:57:40.480
in thinking about
the ways in which you

00:57:40.480 --> 00:57:43.450
can reach a wide audience
and transform society, and at

00:57:43.450 --> 00:57:45.310
the same time, do
well for yourself,

00:57:45.310 --> 00:57:49.000
and then return that
value onto society.

00:57:49.000 --> 00:57:51.240
