the net worth was increased

00:58:22.780 --> 00:58:26.290
in the US based on the economic
output, based on these people,

00:58:26.290 --> 00:58:27.250
and also their legacy?

00:58:27.250 --> 00:58:29.888
Because most likely in the
future, we'll re-look into this

00:58:29.888 --> 00:58:31.680
