really go into the places

00:59:22.280 --> 00:59:24.080
where a capitalist can't go.

00:59:24.080 --> 00:59:26.902
But there is a net positive
on our society because of it.

00:59:26.902 --> 00:59:28.610
And that's kind of
the job of government,

00:59:28.610 --> 00:59:30.560
to do the stuff that
individuals can't

00:59:30.560 --> 00:59:33.120
do for the net positive
of the society.

00:59:33.120 --> 00:59:34.610
So I think there is a lot of--

00:59:34.610 --> 00:59:36.530
