01:04:19.835 --> 01:04:21.460
The military's control
of these sectors

01:04:21.460 --> 01:04:26.740
is infinitesimally small now,
because they've been stood up,

01:04:26.740 --> 01:04:28.270
and the military buys them back.

01:04:28.270 --> 01:04:31.210
So that's a different kind
of way for DARPA to operate.

