01:25:15.370 --> 01:25:18.037
RASHEED: I would say
generally, because DARPA--

01:25:18.037 --> 01:25:19.870
you have a model that's
established already.

01:25:19.870 --> 01:25:20.620
STEPH: OK.

01:25:20.620 --> 01:25:23.215
The reason I ask that
is because in one

01:25:23.215 --> 01:25:24.340
