the government

01:25:32.627 --> 01:25:34.390
to not touch engineers at all.

01:25:34.390 --> 01:25:38.252
He said, "If the US wants
[INAUDIBLE] jobs, better lives,

01:25:38.252 --> 01:25:40.210
and a stronger economy,
the best thing lobbyist

01:25:40.210 --> 01:25:42.943
bureaucrats and politicians
