01:25:42.943 --> 01:25:44.860
And so that's why I
thought it was interesting

01:25:44.860 --> 01:25:46.660
if you were asking in
the context of DARPA

01:25:46.660 --> 01:25:49.030
or in the context of an
organization that was funded

01:25:49.030 --> 01:25:50.470
by government dollars.

01:25:50.470 --> 01:25:53.860
Because maybe what
the implication

01:25:53.860 --> 01:25:55.900
is, in this instance,
for this person who

01:25:55.900 --> 01:25:58.000
is rejecting the notion
that government played

01:25:58.000 --> 01:26:00.370
any role in the computational
revolution of all,

01:26:00.370 --> 01:26:02.740
is we don't want
government help.

01:26:02.740 --> 01:26:05.590
But maybe the model
that they actually want

01:26:05.590 --> 01:26:09.910
is give us the money, and then
don't mess with us at all.

01:26:09.910 --> 01:26:11.050
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

